
1. sw1  sw2 修改默认路由并修改vlan 102 到ISP2
sw1：
undo ip route-static vpn-instance WAN-LAN 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 10.100.2.26 
ip route-static vpn-instance ISP2 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 10.100.29.52 description 2SN_WC_vlan1622

interface Vlanif102
 description JH2SN_internet_IP-office
 ip binding vpn-instance ISP2
 ip address 61.174.15.198 255.255.255.224
 ip address 101.69.105.198 255.255.255.224 sub
 ip address 117.149.38.70 255.255.255.224 sub
 vrrp vrid 102 virtual-ip 61.174.15.193
 vrrp vrid 102 virtual-ip 101.69.105.193
 vrrp vrid 102 virtual-ip 117.149.38.65
 vrrp vrid 102 priority 120
 vrrp vrid 102 preempt-mode timer delay 180

sw2:
ip route-static vpn-instance ISP2 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 10.100.29.52 description 2SN_WC_vlan1622

interface Vlanif102
 description LINK  JH2SN_internet_IP-office
 ip binding vpn-instance ISP2
 ip address 61.174.15.199 255.255.255.224
 ip address 101.69.105.199 255.255.255.224 sub
 ip address 117.149.38.71 255.255.255.224 sub
 vrrp vrid 102 virtual-ip 61.174.15.193
 vrrp vrid 102 virtual-ip 101.69.105.193
 vrrp vrid 102 virtual-ip 117.149.38.65
 vrrp vrid 102 priority 110
 
 
2. 2sn wc 增加到sw1 sw2 vlan 1622 的虚拟ip 路由

ip route-static 61.174.15.192 255.255.255.224 10.100.29.51 description YOUZU_SW_vlan1622
ip route-static 101.69.105.192 255.255.255.224 10.100.29.51 description YOUZU_SW_vlan1622
ip route-static 117.149.38.64 255.255.255.224 10.100.29.51 description YOUZU_SW_vlan1622

3. 2sn WC 上 去掉 

undo ip route-static 61.174.15.192 255.255.255.224 10.100.2.18 
undo ip route-static 101.69.105.192 255.255.255.224 10.100.2.18 
undo ip route-static 117.149.38.64 255.255.255.224 10.100.2.18 
 

验证：
把自己的电脑切换到2枢纽出口 看能否正常上网并同时查看监控上的2SN图表。


4. 2枢纽wc sw2  vlan 1623 清除  sw1 vlan1623 不能清除，因为是连接2sn lc的！
undo int vlan 1623

==============================

5. nqa track 上联

undo nqa test-instance JH2SN JH2SN1623

nqa test-instance JH2SN JH2SN1622
 test-type icmp
 destination-address ipv4 10.100.29.51
 records result 10
 records history 100
 sendpacket passroute
 fail-percent 60
 frequency 5
 interval seconds 1
 timeout 1
 ttl 1
 vpn-instance ISP2
 source-interface Vlanif102
 start now
 
 
 






